<ul>
<li>All tours and entrance fees included</li>
<li>Services of Explorer Guide.</li>
<li>7 nights at the 4 star Hotel Ramada in Graz.</li>
<li>Half board included throughout the tour.</li>
<li>Pumpkin seed oil factory guided tour and tasting.</li>
<li>Schneeberger winery visit, guided tour and wine tasting.</li>
<li>Half day city tour of Graz.</li>
<li>Lipizzaner stud farm of Piber visit and guided tour.</li>
<li>Steam Train ride from Stainz to Preding.</li>
<li>Stübing Open Air Museum entrance.</li>
<li>Gösser Brewery and museum guided tour and beer tasting</li>
